<li class='cover' id='bookCover_58474450'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/58474450-wisdom-from-the-lives-and-letters-of-st-francis-de-sales-and-jane-de-cha"><img alt="Wisdom from the Lives and Letters of St Francis de Sales and Jane de Chantal" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/book/111x148-bcc042a9c91a29c1d680899eff700a03.png" />
